{"tid":2068800,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星,解放軍用狼牙棒都唔用特殊兵諸葛連弩","createTime":"2020-06-18T03:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:22:00.000Z","uid":8968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65f0e85fe18d009dae4b670a49074f44ba1fa224","tid":2068800,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201701/c8d76ec3b37d632d5e07aff05f2018e2.PNG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201701%2Fc8d76ec3b37d632d5e07aff05f2018e2.PNG%3Fw%3D1000&h=6bcf2b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓練成本：40木材、35黃金<br />\n升級精銳花費：760食物、760黃金<br />\n基礎生命值：45<br />\n傷害：8 (穿透屬性)<br />\n*對槍兵系+2<br />\n<br />\n簡介：諸葛弩手是徒步弓兵單位，雖然射程短、但是可以密集射出箭矢。<br />\n諸葛弩手通常後方會搭配僧侶(Monk)以及弩砲(Scorpion)，對於近距離單位的殺傷是很可觀的，如果敵方行動速度低，則更加有效。與步兵協同作戰時，諸葛弩手十分出色。此外，諸葛弩手用在保護城堡(Castle)也是十分優秀的。雖然他們並無法增加城堡的攻擊力，但由於其使用大量箭矢的攻擊特性，讓他們成為衝撞車(Ram)的剋星。<br />\n也因此，諸葛弩手在面對大部分反弓兵單位如：哥德衛隊(Huskarl)、戰矛兵(Skirmisher)時表現也不差。還是能藉由強大密集的射擊稍稍壓制。不過就效率而言諸葛弩還是應該避免遭遇這些單位。尤其是射程比諸葛弩更遠的遠距部隊，打帶跑是最令諸葛弩手頭痛的戰術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/9I7UfTAXAV6ptV9OWyjheBTQSZMDIjbND7OZteFDPmEuKH9Ws9Wk9pT6RcCg5DWeUPc2Mmrd0TBdniQ5UUwa_olE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F9I7UfTAXAV6ptV9OWyjheBTQSZMDIjbND7OZteFDPmEuKH9Ws9Wk9pT6RcCg5DWeUPc2Mmrd0TBdniQ5UUwa_olE&h=671a68d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n竟然用返民兵, 係咪仲係黑暗時代???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f4b7780ee16739451d5b9ad5c36710eb7b8cdb","tid":2068800,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"大象兵血高"},{"pid":"f471e8a28bb93208f51d2b8ab179511ca0b1b4f3","tid":2068800,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60f4b7780ee16739451d5b9ad5c36710eb7b8cdb","tid":2068800,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"大象兵血高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:15:08.000Z","msg":"人地今次出村民咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca59bd0b8cf67bd55ecb60eb9691d078c6b61c1","tid":2068800,"uid":182660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"劣質民兵打印度村民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}